---
title: Garlic Chicken & Creamy Lemon Spaghetti with Peas & Scallions
description: Garlicky seared chicken sits atop pea-studded spaghetti tossed in creamy lemon sauce—a zesty, satisfying dish that transports you straight to the trattoria. Top these loaded pasta bowls with scallion greens, lemon zest, and a final squeeze of fresh lemon juice, then twirl in that lucky fork for a 20-minute meal that can’t be beat.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/660c63759149ba03ec9b06ad-21460236.jpeg
